data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence, where modern elegance meets comfort in every corner. Nestled within a serene neighborhood, this home offers the perfect blend of functionality and style. Step inside to discover an open concept layout designed to impress. The vaulted family room welcomes you with its grandeur, featuring a charming brick fireplace that adds warmth and character to the space. The heart of the home is the gourmet kitchen, equipped with sleek stainless steel appliances, a convenient breakfast bar, and a delightful breakfast room overlooking the backyard oasis. Whether you're entertaining guests or enjoying a casual meal with family, this kitchen is sure to inspire your culinary endeavors. Retreat to the luxurious primary bedroom on the main level, boasting a tray ceiling, not one but two walk-in closets, and a spa-like ensuite bathroom complete with a double vanity, jetted soaking tub, and a separate shower for indulgent relaxation. The split bedroom plan ensures privacy and convenience, with additional bedrooms providing ample space for family members or guests. Venture downstairs to the partially finished basement, offering endless possibilities for recreation, hobbies, or storage to suit your needs. Step outside, where a covered front porch welcomes you home and a large back patio beckons for outdoor gatherings. A charming pergola adds a touch of sophistication to the outdoor space, creating the perfect setting for enjoying sunny days and starry nights. With its thoughtful design, luxurious amenities, and prime location, this home is ready to fulfill your every desire. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours and experience the ultimate in modern living! Ask how you can receive up to $1500 credit by using one of our preferred lenders. Exclusions may apply.
